parameters:
\SE[14]... Wait, she ran away!! And this isn't a dead end,
right...!? Plus, I left Laura behind...!

\SE[10]If it's Laura-san (probably), it'll be fine!
\!\SE[10]And besides, it's not a dead end!!

\SE[16]You can see it, right?! The beautiful scenery
outside!! \!\SE[12]Jump from the middle window! \.Surprise!
\.And then...

\SE[29]You're planning to push me into the river, aren't
you...!! \SE[12]I can already see through your intentions!!

\SE[14]How did you know...!! \SE[15]But, let's get straight
to the point! \.Alright!\.\SE[16]Those who are ready, please
go ahead!!

\SE[2]Lunaroa is going too...? \SE[0]Yeah, let's go together
then.

\SE[14]H-He really jumped...!! \!\SE[27]Where does he get
that determination from...!?

\SE[14]Ryan-san! What will you do!? \SE[13]Will you show
your manly spirit...!? \SE[16]Or will you go with ladies
first...!?
\SE[14]If you say that, then there's no choice but to go...!

\SE[2]So you're not good with heights, huh? \!\SE[0]Well,
don't worry. \.If anything happens, \.I'll catch you down
below.

\SE[14] (Oh no... Ryan-san, you're quite mischievous...
\SE[20] Surprisingly, you're a bit of a trickster...)

\SE[14]Alright! Rebecca-san!! \SE[13]Decide your resolve and
jump before the pursuers come!! \SE[16]Ryan-san is waiting
too!!

\SE[11]I understand...! \!\SE[12]I just have to jump,
right...! If I jump...!!

\SE[56]Get ready... Rebecca... \!\SE[42]I'm a capable
girl... I'll do my best...!
